node.text:
Welcome to another segment of the Weekly Forecast!

Venus is interacting with Neptune on Monday, which may bring some new feelings of romance – just be sure those romantic emotions are rooted in reality. Communicative Mercury is interacting with abundant Jupiter on Tuesday, making it an ideal day to expand your mind and learn new things. The Moon is void of course on Wednesday, meaning that motivation and focus may be hard to find. 
 
✨ What will the rest of the week hold? Find out in the Weekly Forecast with Terence.
 
Claim your FREE astrological reading 👉 https://bit.ly/38du0Qc
Speak with Terence 👉 https://bit.ly/2Grl1De
